  Locus:
    Page: 119
    Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Ego
---
Egoism makes one see glory in petty achievements, happiness in trivial
acquisitions, joy in temporary authority over others. But, the Immortal in
him is awaiting discovery to confer bliss and liberation from birth and
death.
